---
import { AppConfig } from "../../data";
---

<section class="Slide">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="content">
            <p class="content-title">Brand Voice in practice</p>
            <ol class="grid-ol">
                <li>
                    <span>✅ Direct. We say what we mean without padding. "We build web apps" not "We leverage cutting-edge technologies."</span>
                    <span>❌ Hype-driven. No "revolutionary," "disrupting," "world-class" unless backed by evidence.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>✅ Confident, not arrogant. We know our work is excellent. We let the outcomes prove it.</span>
                    <span>❌ Jargon-heavy. We write for founders and operators, not engineers reviewing our CV.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>✅ "We build custom software for businesses that have outgrown generic tools and can't afford another failed project."</span>
                    <span>❌ "We leverage innovative, cutting-edge solutions to help visionary businesses achieve their digital transformation goals."</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>✅ "We'll build you a system that brings in more leads every month — and we'll show you the numbers."</span>
                    <span>❌ "Our cutting-edge, synergistic solutions leverage best-in-class technology frameworks."</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>✅ "Your website should be your best salesperson — working 24/7 even when you're asleep."</span>
                    <span>❌ "We holistically transform stakeholder digital journeys across enterprise touchpoints."</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>✅ "Here's exactly what we'll build, why, and what result you should expect. Shall we start?"</span>
                    <span>❌ "We'll scope the engagement and revert with a comprehensive strategic deliverable roadmap."</span>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
